messages.text: Eve?
Oh my God, what’s going on?? Did they get them out yet??
Anton sent a text that not all of them made it out
Like some are still stuck in there??
Like some are…dead
WHAT HAPPENED TO ADRIENNE
I don’t know yet. I’m waiting for the cars to pull up
I just wanted you to prepare yourself
You know it would’ve been easier for you to just tell me one way or another.
Now I feel like I’m going to throw up
I’m sorry, but I had to say it now too because...
there is something else we need to think about here if she is safe
What?
I don’t think we can take Adrienne back to the US
WHAT DO YOU MEAN!? WHAT WAS THE POINT!?
She won’t be safe. That is one thing these Lazarus idiots got right
So what the hell are you suggesting then?
Jess’s guy said he knows someone who can relocate these girls...
and make them kind of go off the map
No, just bring her back here. Maybe we can just cut her hair etc
They’ll come looking for her, and you know it.
If she’s anywhere near you or your family, they will know where to look for her
Where will he send her??
I don’t know.
But I mean anywhere is better than where she can be hunted all the time
How do you expect me to agree to this after how long she was missing.
Now that I can finally get her back, I have to let her go?
Maybe not forever, but now is not smart.
What does Jess think about this? I bet she told you to fuck off
About Jess…
Yeah?
Anton told me she didn’t make it out
No…that can’t be right.
She probably is just hiding and slipped out or something.
He thinks she’s dead in the building. After she found the girls...
there apparently was an altercation with one of the guards.
Either way, we can’t focus on that right now.
We need to make a decision, because since there was a riot there, we don’t know if
anyone caught them on camera or anything, so they’re not safe here either.
Before Jess went…the foundation where they got smuggled into…
she had The Monkey drain that philanthropist’s bank account.
There was a lot of money.
So all of them can have good lives set up all over the world, elsewhere.
Incognito.
Eve?
Yeah…
So we’re on the same page?
I didn’t say that…and we don’t even know if Adrienne's alive right now so…
The first car is here!!
Is Adrienne on it????
No…
I don’t think I can take it if she’s dead, Anna.
The other cars just pulled up…
I’m almost afraid to ask
Well?
Anna?
Eve?? Guess who??
What do you mean?
Oh my God!!! ADRIENNE!!!!!
Are you okay?? Did they hurt you??
What is on your head??
It’s a hood! I’m okay!
Your friend, and these guys helped us get out before anything happened
Did they make you take anything??
Just some pills when we first got there, but I think that’s out of my system mostly.
Thank God for your friend Jess.
You have no idea how much I’ve missed you! We all thought you were dead.
Please know that I kept looking for you, before now too
I know you did.
I once tried to send you a postcard in the mail, but the guy who took me caught me
I don’t even think I can look Mom and Dad in the face again.
They didn’t say ANYTHING.
They didn’t know the extent of it. None of us did.
And we can tell them now, and just go back to normal.
I just want to be back in my own bed. Did they keep my room the same?
Eve?
Adrienne, you can’t come home.
What do you mean??
It’s not safe for you here
But where will I go?
I don’t know. One of Jess’s guys is going to take you to a safe place to start over
But how will I get in touch with you??
They’ll tell you that, and if I’m allowed, and when it’s safe I’ll come to visit you
I just want to come home though
I know. I want you home, but you know this is the first place they’ll look for you.
They’ve already come to the house to see if -
Eve, it’s Anna again
Somebody who is part of the experiments spotted them and tailed them here.
Anton’s guy said they have to leave now, so they can get them where they need to go
Can I talk to her again??
No we have to go
Can you make sure that she stays with Emily??
Emily didn’t come back either. We have to go. I’ll be in touch soon
Wait!! What if they aren’t taking them where they say they are!
ANNA!!!
four hours later
He took them all, and dropped me at the airport
That’s it?? You don’t know where he took them??
No.
He didn’t even give you a general idea?
He said that he’s scattering them all over. This way they aren’t conspicuous.
Will he be able to tell us how to get in touch??
No
HOW DID YOU LET HIM JUST TAKE HER LIKE THAT THEN??
I think things will be okay.
HOW DO YOU KNOW??
Hope.
A few months later after radio silence, Eve starts to receive several messages from destinations all over the world.
Adrienne has given the other girls Eve's number, and they ask Eve to tell their mothers, fathers, sisters, brothers, girlfriends and boyfriends that they are okay.
The last of these messages that Eve receives is this:
Eve, there’s not a Burger King milkshake for miles where I am.
I slipped out before everyone with Emily.
(I needed to escape some things back in the states, too.)
If you ever knew my last name, you’d be able to look up the warrants, but I’ll leave it a mystery, because that’s more fun ;D
Anton managed to connect us with Adrienne, and we’re doing just fine.
The Monkey will be in touch with exact coordinates in the future.
Join us, yeah?
